title: Newmarket LGBT Late Night Party
description:
Newmarket LGBT Late Night Party with Cheryl Hole and DJ Jack Aird

Come join us on a night to remember with a late night party at Newmarket’s number 1 venue. 

Enjoy a night of tunes by DJ Jack Aird, a resident DJ of Cambridge’s LGBT Night GlitterBomb and DJ at many Pride 🏳️‍🌈 events across the country. Plus a very special guest: Cheryl Hole one of the country’s best drag queens.

VIP Packages available, message the page if your interested. Must be 18 – normal admission policy applies.
